<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>James Haskell has revealed his wife Chloe Madeley thinks he's 'slept with 1,000 women' in the past.</p>

<p>In a new interview, the former rugby union player, 35, admitted he said 'the standard response of 12' when the personal trainer, 33, asked about his sexual history and insisted he 'didn't need to go into details' about his past.</p>

<p>The I'm A Celebrity star also shared that the couple, who will celebrate their second wedding anniversary in December, will try for a baby 'once they have a settled income stream'. </p>

<p>'I don't need to go into details of the past!' James Haskell has revealed his wife Chloe Madeley thinks he's 'slept with 1,000 women' in the past</p>

<p>James said: 'Chloe claims that I've slept with 1,000 women. My wife and I did the numbers game and I was having absolutely no part in it. </p>

<p>'Instead I said the standard response of 12 — no more, and no less. All that stuff, it's completely irrelevant. Do I need to go into the minutiae of details of the past? No. </p>

<p>'Chloe and I have a relationship of trust. Though Chloe also claims every time she goes to the gym I watch porn... [but] whenever she goes to type in YouTube on her phone it comes up YouPorn.'</p>

<p>Cheeky! In a new interview, the former rugby union player, 35, admitted he said 'the standard response of 12' when the personal trainer, 33, asked about his sexual history</p>

<p>The media personality added to The Sun that the pair discussed the topic of children for the first time during the coronavirus lockdown.</p>

<p>He said that while the the celebrity offspring was 'previously undecided' on the prospect of starting a family, she has now changed her tune and shows the TV star 'a lot of baby pictures' in her spare time. </p>

<p>The sportsman also shed light on their relationship, confessing that they considered couples therapy in the past and have their 'ups and downs'. </p>

<p>Broody? The I'm A Celebrity star also shared that the couple, who will celebrate their second wedding anniversary in December, will try for a baby 'once they have a settled income stream' </p>

<p>Elsewhere in the discussion, the DJ recalled when he discovered she was 'The One' as she 'harangued' hospital stuff to stay by his side during his recovery from surgery. </p>

<p>Earlier this month, Chloe admitted it 'hurt' when she was accused of nepotism because she is the daughter of TV legends Richard Madeley and Judy Finnigan.</p>

<p>The fitness enthusiast told how people thought she got advancements in her career due to her family connections, which she feels she did.</p>

<p>'I would encourage anyone to do it': The sportsman shed light on their relationship, confessing that they considered couples therapy in the past and have their 'ups and downs'</p>

<p>Speaking to Radio Times, she said: 'I was accused of nepotism because I was Richard and Judy's daughter. It was true, therefore it hurt. Now I've built up my own thing, I feel a lot stronger.'</p>

<p>The blonde got her start in TV as a roaming reporter on shows that her parents presented and later appeared as a contestant on Dancing on Ice in 2011.</p>

<p>She later became a contestant on The Jump and has also regularly appeared on the small screen for her work in the fitness industry. </p>

<p>Chloe and James have created a new podcast called Couples Quarantine focusing on the challenges faced by couples who are now living and working at home. </p>

